OL,3,CDiscipline policies are not fit for
OL,4,Cthe 21st century, says former Chief
OL,5,CWhip
OL,7,FThe way that political parties deal
OL,8,Fwith serious problems such as poor or
OL,9,Fcriminal behaviour by MPs isn't "fit
OL,10,Ffor the 21st century" according to the
OL,11,Fformer UK Government Chief Whip and
OL,12,FWelsh Secretary, Simon Hart.
OL,14,FMr Hart was the MP for Carmarthen West
OL,15,Fand South Pembrokeshire until the 2024
OL,16,FUK General Election. He's just
OL,17,Fpublished a diary of his time in the
OL,18,Fcabinets of Boris Johnson and Rishi
OL,19,FSunak, first as Welsh Secretary, then
OL,20,Fas Chief Whip.
