OL,3,CDiscipline policies are not fit for
OL,4,Cthe 21st century, says former Chief
OL,5,CWhip
OL,7,FHe says that, "the Whip's office is
OL,8,Fnot a counselling centre, it's not a
OL,9,Ffirm of solicitors, it's not a
OL,10,Fdoctor's surgery. There are lots of
OL,11,Fthings we're not. What we were there
OL,12,Fto do was to get the government's
OL,13,Fbusiness done. And I think it made us
OL,14,Fall a bit nervous that we were being
OL,15,Fasked to deal with some very
OL,16,Fcomplicated, very tragic, in some
OL,17,Fcases, issues."
