OL,7,FAsked if he thinks that the system
OL,8,Fshould change, Mr Hart says,
OL,9,F"Absolutely. I think the system is not
OL,10,F... I don't think it's fit for the
OL,11,F21st century.
OL,13,F"There's a lot of, you know, 'nudge,
OL,14,Fnudge' and all that around what the
OL,15,FWhip's office does and the power that
OL,16,Fit exerts. That's all fine and it does
OL,17,Fmake for a good story (but) I don't
OL,18,Fthink it necessarily makes a good
OL,19,Fworking place in 2025.
